{"id":480413374,"lang":"python3","time":"7 months, 1 week","timestamp":1618376466,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"44 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/480413374/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Zigzag Conversion","memory":"14.3 MB","code":"class Solution(object):\n    def convert(self, s, numRows):\n        if numRows == 1:\n            return s \n        n = len(s)\n        cycle = 2*numRows - 2\n        strlist = []\n        for i in range(numRows):\n            for j in range(i, n, cycle):\n                strlist.append(s[j])\n                if i != numRows-1 and i != 0 and j+cycle-2*i < n:\n                    strlist.append(s[j+cycle-2*i])             \n        newstr = ''.join(strlist)\n        return newstr","compare_result":"","title_slug":"zigzag-conversion"}
